asset.hookText:
The SmokePro SE Pellet Grill is built so you can discover the real tastes of award winning BBQ right from your own back patio. Simply select the desired cooking temperature and let the electronic controls maintain temperatures for you. Cooking temperatures range from 160°F up to 500°F, including low or high smoke settings. The built in grease management system keeps things clean for the next barbecue. Utility shelf added for convenience.
